Information Subject Rights
Upon request, we will grant your request for access, rectification, cancellation, or objection in relation to your Personal Information, subject to verifying the identity of the person submitting such a request. We may deny access or refuse your request under the following circumstances:
Where the rights of a third party are adversely affected;
Where there is a legal reason or decision of a competent authority restricting access or not allowing the rectification, cancellation, or objection;
Or where the rectification, cancellation, or objection has been previously performed.
Revoking Consent
You may revoke your express consent for the use of your Personal information at any time by contacting us and providing sufficient information so that we can comply with your request. This request must clearly detail the information or purposes for which your consent is revoked.
Transfer of information
Your Personal information may be transferred to third parties or outside of Mexico to offer you goods or services in accordance with your use of the Site.
